471
00:28:00,863 --> 00:28:02,066
Estes são para o professor Prince.

472
00:28:02,066 --> 00:28:06,143
Mas eu realmente não consigo terminar todos eles, Aou.

473
00:28:06,276 --> 00:28:07,202
Ver?

474
00:28:07,202 --> 00:28:08,422
Vamos comer juntos.

475
00:28:08,422 --> 00:28:09,322
Certo?

476
00:28:09,484 --> 00:28:11,218
