519
00:30:57,492 --> 00:30:59,700
(Merda! Precisamos ir agora.)

520
00:30:59,700 --> 00:31:00,904
(Seus homens estão nos observando.)

521
00:31:00,994 --> 00:31:02,444
Espere.

522
00:31:02,444 --> 00:31:03,460
Mesa!

523
00:31:08,508 --> 00:31:09,482
Aou!

524
00:31:15,801 --> 00:31:16,827
Peguei vocês.

525
00:31:17,310 --> 00:31:19,044
